    <item>
      <title>由于成本上升，Fortescue 利润低于预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-27/fortescue-s-profit-edges-higher-as-shrugs-off-china-downturn</link>
      <description><![CDATA[福蒂斯丘有限公司 (Fortescue Ltd.) 公布全年利润小幅增长，​​但这家第四大铁矿石生产商的利润未达分析师预期，原因是该公司面临通胀压力，同时还面临着最大客户中国对钢铁原料需求放缓的影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-27/fortescue-s-profit-edges-higher-as-shrugs-off-china-downturn</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 27 Aug 2024 22:49:35 GMT</pubDate>
